        <details class="group ring-1 ring-inset ring-hairline rounded-xl bg-canvas overflow-hidden shadow-lvl2">
          <summary class="w-full px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between text-left font-sans text-sm font-bold text-ink cursor-pointer list-none marker:hidden hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 transition-colors">
            <span>What is the Longest Common Subsequence (LCS) algorithm?</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-mute transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
