          <div class="border-t border-hairline px-6 py-4 bg-canvas-soft">
            <p class="text-body text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">The LCS algorithm is a classic computer science method used to find the longest subsequence common to two sequences. It is the mathematical backbone of version control systems like Git and diffing utilities, helping determine the minimal number of insertions and deletions needed to transform one text into another.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
